Package: regexpert
Title: Toolkit for Human-Readable and Expert Regular Expressions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Oliphant", , "jonathanoliphant13@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simplifies the creation and management of regular expressions 
    through a human-readable domain-specific language. 'regexpert' provides 
    intuitive tools for building patterns, explaining complex regex logic, 
    and integrating seamlessly with tidyverse workflows.
